data.title: Senators unveil bill to keep Trump from easing curbs on AI chip sales to China
data.description: The SAFE CHIPS Act is a rare effort led in part by Trump’s own party to stop him from further relaxing tech export restrictions on Beijing.
data.keywords: China, Pete Ricketts, Dave McCormick, Nvidia, Chris Coons, Russia, H20 AI chips, John Moolenaar, Iran, Beijing, Andy Kim, North Korea, Jeanne Shaheen, Commerce Department
